---
title: Beef in Slow Roasted Tomato Butter Sauce  with smashed potatoes and salad
description: In this recipe, a sumptuous sauce is created when cherry tomatoes are slow-roasted along with all sorts of delicious things such as garlic and butter. When the tomatoes soften, they create a beautiful, buttery and tomato-y mixture that's perfect for coating the succulent beef rump in this dish.
